      <title>芝加哥教育委员会因市长与工会冲突解雇首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/chicago-education-board-fires-ceo-pedro-martinez-after-union-mayor-feud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥教育委员会周五采取了一项非同寻常的举措，解雇了该学区的首席执行官佩德罗·马丁内斯 (Pedro Martinez)，戏剧性地结束了他与市长之间长达数月的争斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/chicago-education-board-fires-ceo-pedro-martinez-after-union-mayor-feud</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 03:56:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新日铁称美国对交易审查施加不当影响：路透社</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/nippon-steel-alleges-undue-us-influence-on-deal-review-reuters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据路透社报道，新日本制铁公司声称白宫对该公司以 149 亿美元收购美国钢铁公司交易的国家安全审查施加了不当影响，并威胁称，如果交易受阻，该公司将采取法律行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/nippon-steel-alleges-undue-us-influence-on-deal-review-reuters</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 02:30:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
